{
  "stem": "18186.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 40.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They wanted us down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They wanted to kill us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had to.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If not, they would come up themselves.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, they said they knew that the ladder is up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The people must be there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they said, if you're not gonna do that, we're going to climb up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We'll find you anyway.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they started-- I don't know even remember who started to move the ladder down.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I stood next to my mother, and in a spare moment, I-- something came into my mind.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I left my mother, and I jumped to the other side of the house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was the [? sukkah. ?]",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I jumped, and after me jumped another-- the young girl, at that time a young-- year younger than I was, and my mother's cousin, a woman maybe in her early 30s.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Do you remember the names of the people that you were with?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The one is Perl, and the other one is Sassel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But she never-- she didn't survive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only Perl and I--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Excuse me, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we came out to the-- outside in the street.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we saw nobody there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we decided to go to climb over the fence, and run-- and to run away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's exactly what we did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I started to go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was the first one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We got out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then that was Ukraine-- the Ukrainian side.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Naturally the Ukrainian, there was children and adults watching what's going on in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They started to chase us, the-- the kids.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they started to yell, there-- there comes the gestapo.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And make arrest, police, Jewish people, Jewish kids running!",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we kept running, and we kept on running.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we decided we'll go to the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
